5. div and span tag - to group things together
<div> is a block level generic container, just like <h1> will create a new line
<span> is a inline group container


6.Attributes (adding additional information to tags)
(key = value)
<src>
<img src = "xxxx.png">  -- for images
<a href = > --for hyperlink
<a href="url">Link text</a>
#<a href="weather.html">go to weather page</a> 也可以是local的网页，但是还是在引号里


7.HTML table
<table border = "1">
	<tr> <!-- tr for each row -->
		<th>name</th> <!-- th for table head -->
		<th>age</th> 
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>carol</td> <!-- td for each cell -->
		<td>22</td>
	</tr>
</table>

---other way no difference in appearance,dintingish for browswer stuff
<table border = "1">
<thead>
	<tr> <!-- tr for each row -->
		<th>name</th> <!-- th for table head -->
		<th>age</th> 
	</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
	<tr>
		<td>carol</td> <!-- td for each cell -->
		<td>22</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>Kate</td> <!-- td for each cell -->
		<td>23</td>
	</tr>
</tbody>
</table>



